# Testing Rules

Use practical testing that protects real functionality.

## Priorities

Test:

1. Business logic
2. Parsing
3. Persistence
4. Data transformation
5. Regression-prone workflows

## Avoid

- Excessive scaffolding
- Fragile UI tests
- Tests that only verify framework behavior
- Mock-heavy designs that make the app harder to maintain

## Standard

Prefer fewer useful tests over lots of theater.
